# Portal Chat Streaming UI

- Always call `POST /api/chat` with `stream: true`, plus `sessionId`/`conversationId` when available.
- Parse SSE (`text/event-stream`) by splitting events on blank lines and reading `data:` lines.
- Handle `event: done` and `event: error`; ignore keepalive/comment lines safely.
- Update the existing assistant message incrementally as chunks arrive.
- Persist `sessionId` and `conversationId` from the `done` payload for continuity.
